data.description: Description: Never be without electricity in your home again. This home has a whole house generator to make sure your family stays warm with lights on no matter what the weather issues are outside. What is your plan to control rising electrical costs? Solar is the way to go. The seller has done the hard work for you, really it was for themselves but unfortunately they need to move to take care of a family member. Beaming with Pride of ownership at every step. The moment you arrive you can see the impeccable attention to detail. They have added stone and brick planter boxes in the front yard along with a full gutter system, truly exceptional. The peaceful spacious back yard is ready for you and your family to create long lasting memories.
